# 🚀 Getting Started

Clone this repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/Python-Data-Visualization-Handbook.git
```

Move into the project

```bash
cd Python-Data-Visualization-Handbook
```

Install the required libraries

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Launch Jupyter Notebook

```bash
jupyter notebook
```

